<li><span class="citation book">White, Gregory (2003). <i>All-in-one Security+ Certification Exam Guide</i>. Emeryville, CA: McGraw-Hill/Osborne. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0-07-222633-1" title="Special:BookSources/0-07-222633-1">0-07-222633-1</a>.</span></li>
